<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">ifndef stackPtr<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;stackPtr = $0500<br />endif<br /><br />macro pushStack <br />&nbsp; &nbsp;ldx stackPtr<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;inx<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta stackPtr, x&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;stx stackPtr<br />endm<br /><br />macro pullStack<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;ldx stackPtr<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;lda stackPtr, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;dex&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;stx stackPtr<br />endm<br /></div></div>

